##  Please note: not all of the individual control style customizations have been provided    #
##  here, because it would be too exhaustive. Contact me (Neo) for details of specifics.      #
##                                                                                            #
##  All the entries in a styling file are optional. If an entry is not present while loading, #
##  the tool will pickup the corresponding internal style.                                    #
